<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>depends on how much they decrease PoP xp...<br>
<br>
currently for every 100xp in a 2 person group you split 102xp so 51xp per person<br>
<br>
if they didn't nerf xp at all, you split 120xp so 60xp per person<br>
<br>
a 5% nerf:<br>
95xp -&gt; 114xp -&gt; 57xp per person - still better<br>
<br>
10% nerf:<br>
90xp -&gt; 108xp -&gt; 54xp per person - still better<br>
<br>
15% nerf:<br>
85xp -&gt; 102xp -&gt; 51xp per person - exactly the same<br>
<br>
&gt;15% nerf: duo groups are hurt.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
